# Enforce LF line endings in the repo AND on checkout. Without this, Git's
# core.autocrlf=true (the Windows default) smudges text files to CRLF on
# checkout, which makes `biome check` (LF) fail — breaking `npm run check`
# and therefore `prepublishOnly`/`npm publish`. eol=lf overrides autocrlf.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets — never normalize.
*.png  binary
*.jpg  binary
*.jpeg binary
*.webp binary
*.ico  binary
